        "subject": "LU-1095 mdc: quiet mdc_close() debug logging",
        "message": "LU-1095 mdc: quiet mdc_close() debug logging\n\nmdc_close() is logging a message for every file open with the D_HA\nmask, which is enabled by default.  This is flooding the debug logs\non the client under normal usage.\n\nSigned-off-by: Andreas Dilger <andreas.dilger@intel.com>\nChange-Id: Ib2e70800b1f4bfb839460b13a58522d7ac3ebbe5\n"
      },
